    "The formulation is given by:CA softmax t = softmax(β • CA t [1:]).",
    "(12)Following the official implementation, we set β = 100 for SD1.4, SD1.5, SD2.1 [1] and SD3.5-M [5] across baseline methods through our experiments (see Secs. 4.2 and F).",
